# circleci_organization (Resource)

Manages a CircleCI organization.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "circleci_organization" "example" {
  name     = "my-org"
  vcs_type = "github"
}
```

<!-- schema generated by tfplugindocs -->
## Schema

### Required

- `name` (String) The name of the organization. Changing this value forces a new resource to be created.
- `vcs_type` (String) The VCS type for the organization (e.g., `github`, `bitbucket`, `circleci`). Changing this value forces a new resource to be created.

### Read-Only

- `id` (String) The unique identifier of the organization.
- `slug` (String) The slug of the organization.

## Import

Import is supported using the organization ID:

```shell
terraform import circleci_organization.example "<organization_id>"
```
